&amp;#xD;
 (PRWEB) January 23, 2004 
DCOMM, a Seattle based company, brings to market the latest Bluetooth hands-free solution from the 4th largest headset manufacturer in the world.  The Bluetrek G2 weighing less than 12 grams achieves an amazing 9-hour talk time with high fidelity sound quality.  This product availiable in the US January [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/bluetooth-marketing-blog/Bluetooth_Marketing_Blog-DCOMM_an_Bluetooth_accessory_company_in_Seattle_WA_recently_announced_the_launch_of_its_second-gener.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>{thumbnail}<br />
&#xD;</p>
<p class="releaseDateline"> (PRWEB) January 23, 2004 </p>
<p>DCOMM, a Seattle based company, brings to market the latest <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> hands-free solution from the 4th largest headset manufacturer in the world.  The Bluetrek G2 weighing less than 12 grams achieves an amazing 9-hour talk time with high fidelity sound quality.  This product availiable in the US January 2004, will have a stylish design with an aggressive price point.</p>
<p>&#xD;</p>
<p>The first product from this same manufacturer, Bluetrek, was one of the few headsets designed to work with all <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >phones</a> irregardless of brand. And its universal <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> Dongle, compatible with both products, opens the door even further to most of the non-<a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >mobile</a> <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >phones</a> on the market today. </p>
<p>&#xD;</p>
<p>Using the latest CSR chipset and a very comprehensive module, the Bluetrek G2 is expected to become one of the top sellers in the <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> headset market this season. &#8220;We are excited about this product because it offers extended talk time (up to 9 hours), light weight (12.5 grams), and a design that is already receiving rave reviews,&#8221; says Scott Dale, Sales &amp; <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Marketing</a> Director of DCOMM. </p>
<p>&#xD;</p>
<p>For more information about Bluetrek or Bluetrek G2 please contact DCOMM at (206)374-1404 or visit the website at www.dalecommunications.com.</p>
<p>&#xD;</p>
