<p>When you are starting a home business and just want to make money online, it can seem frustrating when top network <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >marketing</a> companies keep harping on about goal setting and mental strategies. It&#8217;s the same for much of the internet <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >marketing</a> training you find, they talk about being persistent, determined in terms of what success takes. This article outlines the importance of a person&#8217;s mindset in their ultimate success as an entrepreneur and whether it really is a mind game or just hard work.</p>
