      <description><![CDATA[This mini USB Bluetooth Adapter enables short-range wireless data connectivity between computers and Bluetooth enabled devices. Personal digital assistants, cellular phones, and other devices can connect wirelessly with your computer. It is an open specification for wireless data transmission that operates on the globally available 2.4GHz radio frequency. Bluetooth devices can communicate with each other [...]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41OlRX2ivPL._SL75_.jpg"/>This mini USB <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> Adapter enables short-range <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >wireless</a> data connectivity between computers and <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> enabled devices. Personal digital assistants, cellular <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >phones</a>, and other devices can connect wirelessly with your computer. It is an open specification for <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >wireless</a> data transmission that operates on the globally available 2.4GHz radio frequency. <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> devices can communicate with each other within a 20M range. Transfer up to three times faster than previous <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> versions! Supports: Windows 2000 / XP / Vista Features <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> Specification V2.0 + EDR Data Transfer rate: 3 Mbps / sec Dongle support the following <a href="http://www.bluepodpromoter.co.uk" >Bluetooth</a> Profiles DUN (Dial-Up Network), FTP (FAX / File Transfer), GAP (non-OEM Access), GEOP (non-OEM Object Exchange), HCRP (Hardcopy Cable Replacement), HID (Human Interface Device), HSP (Headset), LAP (LAN Access), PP (Object Push), DAP (Service Discovery Application), SPP (Serial Port), SYNC (Synchronization) Interface: USB V1.1 &#038; 2.0 compatible Power Supply: DC 5V USB</p>
<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Bluetooth-USB-Micro-Adapter-Dongle/dp/B001EBE1LI%3FSubscriptionId%3D17W81AQPV8QEJKSTAP02%26tag%3Dadpods-21%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB001EBE1LI">Visit merchant</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
